CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. B10 reads: "Chi Delta Mu Fraternity Entertains Lavishly - Dr. Carroll Holmes, center rear, and guests. Mrs. Holmes third from left."  Portion of accompanying article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. A7 by Toki Schalk Johnson reads:"Wednesday brought forth the annual dinner dance given by the Chi Delta Mu Fraternity in beautifully decorated New Arena."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six men, including Dr. Carroll Holmes, center rear, and six women, including Mrs. Holmes, third from left, seated at rectangular banquet table for Chi Delta Mu dinner dance in new Arena Supper Club
